Start with 230Vac present → should choose AC, gas off.
Remove 230Vac, D+ present → should switch to 12V heater, gas off.
Remove D+, Solar active and battery above threshold → should switch to Solar/12V heater.
Remove Solar → should go to gas.
While on gas, bring back 230Vac → must switch immediately to AC and shut gas outputs.
Close manual gas valve (force ignition fail) with no AC/D+ → should alarm, then wait 10 min, then retry gas (and instantly stop retrying if AC or D+ appears during the wait).
